title: Philippines GDP From Manufacturing
description: GDP from Manufacturing in Philippines decreased to 760883 PHP Million in the third quarter of 2022 from 902475 PHP Million in the second quarter of 2022. GDP from Manufacturing in Philippines averaged 622311.86 PHP Million from 2000 until 2022, reaching an all time high of 1052103 PHP Million in the fourth quarter of 2021 and a record low of 365732.94 PHP Million in the first quarter of 2000. This page provides the latest reported value for - Philippines Gdp From Manufacturing - plus previous releases, historical high and low, short-term forecast and long-term prediction, economic calendar, survey consensus and news.
author: Philippine Statistics Authority
